  "prompt": "Why was Divya Bharti's death so controversial?",
  "response": "Divya Bharti's death on April 5, 1993, was surrounded by controversy due to several factors. The young and rising Bollywood actress died at the age of 19 after falling from the balcony of her fifth-floor apartment in Mumbai. Here are key reasons why her death remains controversial:\n\n1. **Ambiguous Circumstances:** The details of her fall were unclear, leading to multiple speculations about what actually happened. It was debated whether her death was a result of an accident, suicide, or if foul play was involved.\n\n2. **Sudden and Shocking:** Divya Bharti was at the peak of her career, and her sudden demise was a shock to her fans and the film industry. The unexpected nature of her death led to intense media coverage and widespread conjectures.\n\n3. **Incomplete Investigations:** Despite various theories, the investigations into her death concluded that it was accidental. Some critics and observers felt that the investigations were not thorough and left many questions unanswered.\n\n4. **Rumors and Speculations:** Given her rising star status and her marriage to film producer Sajid Nadiadwala, rumors about possible motives\u2014including alleged jealousy, personal disputes, or industry rivalries\u2014were rampant.\n\n5. **Impact on the Industry:** Her death significantly impacted Bollywood, leaving a void and leading to various conspiracy theories, further fueling rumors about the circumstances of her demise.\n\nThese factors combined to create an atmosphere of uncertainty and speculation, making Divya Bharti's death a point of continuing controversy.",
